text.paragraph:
Drug/Laboratory Test Interactions - Thiazides should be discontinued before carrying out tests for parathyroid function (see 
   PRECAUTIONS, General
).

Metabolic: Electrolyte imbalance (see 
   PRECAUTIONS
), hyperglycemia, glycosuria, hyperuricemia.

Renal: Renal failure, renal dysfunction, interstitial nephritis (see 
   WARNINGS
).
